quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Humne is (Quran) ko shab-e-qadr mei nazil kiya hai
  97,2,Aur tum kya jano kay shab-e-qadr kya hai
  97,3,Shab-e-qadr hazar mahino se zyada behtar hai
  97,4,Farishtey aur rooh(Jibrael) us mein apne Rubb ke izn(permission) se har hukm le kar utarte hai
  97,5,Woh raat sarasar salamati hai tulu e fajr tak